I do not know if this speeds it up, but here is the (hopefully) same function in fewer lines:
```
def _getRoot(self, cond=None):
    obj = self
    while obj is not None:
        if cond is not None:
            if cond(obj):
                break
        obj = obj._getParent()
    return obj
```

